title: ICE / KIM POST TENT barks
description: Kim barks after you have RETURNETH from the TENT.

dialogueTree.title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Right. I don't really want to hear..."
dialogueTree.english: "Right. I don't really want to hear about what happened in the tent. Let's get going."
dialogueTree.polish: „W porządku. Naprawdę nie chcę słyszeć o tym, co działo się w tym namiocie. Ruszajmy już”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "У парадку. Сапраўды не хачу чуць пра тое, што адбывалася ў той палатцы. Пайшлі ўжо".
